title: Episode 195: From Appetizer to Entree (Feat. Donna & Alex of Black Ink Crew)
itunes:title: Episode 195: From Appetizer to Entree (Feat. Donna & Alex of Black Ink Crew)
description:
Donna and Alex from Black Ink Crew join the ladies of Lip Service this week and cover topics including: going from the side piece to the main, being givers and takers in the bedroom, Donna taking Alex on his first 'baecation,' and much more! Alex opens up about his issues with Ceaser, the status of his back injury, and whether he'll be on Black Ink Crew moving forward. Enjoy!
